# Transform Airports AI Council — API keys
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored) and fill in what you use.
# The CLI loads `.env` automatically at startup; you can also export these
# in your shell instead — a shell export wins over the .env value.

# Anthropic API key — OPTIONAL.
# Leave this unset to bill runs against your Claude.ai subscription
# (sign in once with `claude login`). Set it to bill pay-as-you-go
# against your Anthropic API console balance instead.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# OpenAI API key — only required if you seat the Deep Research lens
# (it runs on OpenAI's deep-research model and bills to your OpenAI account).
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
